# Hello Notion Stack

- **Backend**: Kotlin + Spring Boot 3.x under `backend/` or `apps/backend/`. Use controller, service, repository, model packages. Follow kotlin-spring-boot patterns.
- **Frontend**: Next.js App Router under `frontend/` or `apps/frontend/`. Use app/, components/, lib/. Follow vercel-react-best-practices.
- Keep API contracts and env (e.g. `NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL`) consistent between FE and BE.
